{"tid":983541,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"婚姻無效定離婚","createTime":"2019-01-16T04:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T01:58:47.000Z","uid":27221,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4ac6c04c41fee666e8afb8cad03dbe19f3b6ce4f","tid":983541,"uid":27221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T04:55:48.000Z","msg":"如果係為左某啲原因而去註冊, 結婚簽左紙兩年<br />\n婚後其實無一齊住, 無實際夫妻關係<br />\n而家雙方同意離婚 唔打算分家產 膽養費<br />\n應該申請婚姻無效定離婚<br />\n<br />\n如將來再結婚, 個婚姻狀態都係上次婚姻無效or離婚? <br />\n點都唔會係單身?<br />\n<br />\n謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e64d5b4065a9666df7dfad1540ab104661524e0","tid":983541,"uid":199592,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T04:58:14.000Z","msg":"同大陸人假結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30c0ab9988bb23138bb46152ec0e0b6ff5510e6e","tid":983541,"uid":196924,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T04:58:22.000Z","msg":"間接認自己假結婚?"},{"pid":"b62640326ea86d2348c3430a3fe6986ff7345608","tid":983541,"uid":90820,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T04:59:06.000Z","msg":"等警察幫你查下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13506a223d5fa2a6941fd71e94e8a90af95b5f41","tid":983541,"uid":22974,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T05:00:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77e17a337a2e3e8060025a8f43504931f88d4fd9","tid":983541,"uid":27221,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T05:00:25.000Z","msg":"唔係假結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad1db29bb0b35674a429f22d82aa02224b62a89","tid":983541,"uid":27221,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T05:02:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4a51d938528ff5ad8a2ac85c875c053020b7a4","tid":983541,"uid":61589,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"cit